org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.operators.layouting.util

Class LVertex

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.api.java.tuple.Tuple
      • org.apache.flink.api.java.tuple.Tuple5<GradoopId,Vector,Integer,List<GradoopId>,Vector>
        • org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.operators.layouting.util.LVertex
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, SimpleGraphElement

    public class LVertex
extends org.apache.flink.api.java.tuple.Tuple5<GradoopId,Vector,Integer,List<GradoopId>,Vector>
implements SimpleGraphElement
    Lightweight/Layouting-Vertex. Has all properties of an EPGMVertex that are important for the layouting. This way we do not need to drag around a full Vertex through every operation.
    See Also:
